      <title>英国通胀低于预期促使交易员加大降息押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/uk-inflation-falls-more-than-forecast-to-1-7-lowest-since-2021</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国通胀率三年多来首次跌破英国央行 2% 的目标，促使投资者押注未来几个月英国央行将加快降息步伐。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/uk-inflation-falls-more-than-forecast-to-1-7-lowest-since-2021</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 06:06:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>油价企稳，关注中东风险和中国需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/crude-oil-advances-with-middle-east-risks-and-china-in-focus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价在周二暴跌后维持在每桶 74 美元附近，因为交易员继续关注中东局势升级的风险和明年的前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/crude-oil-advances-with-middle-east-risks-and-china-in-focus</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 23:34:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Rightmove 称英国房东正在以创纪录的速度出售房屋</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/uk-landlords-are-selling-up-at-a-record-pace-rightmove-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心更严格的绿色规则以及即将到来的预算中税收增加的前景，英国买房出租的房东正在以创纪录的数量出售房屋，这给租户带来了进一步的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/uk-landlords-are-selling-up-at-a-record-pace-rightmove-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲股市因盈利疲软而下跌；英镑下跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股市下跌，因为奢侈品行业盈利疲软加剧了人们对半导体行业盈利前景的负面情绪。由于英国通胀率下降刺激人们对降息的押注增加，英镑下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 22:06:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰晤士河危机后，英国监管机构考虑提高投资者回报</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/uk-regulator-weighs-higher-investor-returns-as-thames-woes-bite</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰晤士水务公司危机推高了整个行业的借贷成本后，英国水务监管机构首次考虑提高投资者的回报。]]></description>
